  <brief_title>Efficacy of Symbicort pMDI Administered Once Daily in Adolescents and Adults During 12 Weeks - STEM</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 12 Week, Randomized, Double-Blind, Double-Dummy, Placebo and Active-controlled Study of Symbicort pMDI Administered Once Daily in Adults and Adolescents With Asthma - STEM</official_title>
  <sponsors>
