  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare a dose of Symbicort taken once daily with other
      dosage regimens of Symbicort , budesonide and placebo for the treatment of asthma in
      adolescents and adults
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
